export const size = {
    mobileS: '320px',
    mobileM: '375px',
    mobileL: '425px',
    tablet: '780px',
    laptop: '1200px',
    laptopL: '1440px',
    desktop: '2560px'
  }

export const device = {
    size_mobileS: '320px',
    size_mobileM: '375px',
    size_mobileL: '425px',
    size_tablet: '780px',
    size_laptop: '1200px',
    size_laptopL: '1440px',
    size_desktop: '2560px',

    mobileS: `(min-width: ${size_mobileS})`,
    mobileM: `(min-width: ${size_mobileM})`,
    mobileL: `(min-width: ${size_mobileL})`,
    tablet: `(min-width: ${size_tablet})`,
    laptop: `(min-width: ${size_laptop})`,
    laptopL: `(min-width: ${size_laptopL})`,
    desktop: `(min-width: ${size_desktop})`,
    desktopL: `(min-width: ${size_desktop})`
};

export default device;
